Package com.iflas

Class Phone

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iflas.Phone
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AmanIflasPhone, IflasDeluxePhone, MaximumEffortPhone
    public abstract class Phone
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the base Phone Class. Every phone model derives this class. It holds specification of phone model in string form. Additionally, it holds regional specification of components. It creates model with, base specifications, then regional specifications added in child classes with help of regional component factories.
    Author:
    Furkan KalabalÄ±k
